snippet.title: You Have A Delivery - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3420980/You_Have_A_Delivery/

You Have A Delivery is a stylized, fast-paced FPS action game, inspired by action-comedy films. Take down the mafia in one night: rip apart your enemies, unlock guns and perks, and deliver unstoppable chaos. You're the only one who can pull it off. Can you deliver it?

About CO's: From cracking walnuts to crafting worlds, CO’s is a small team dreaming big—creating unforgettable gaming adventures, one project at a time!

Music: Fuzzeke - Swag Man
